,,28517,1,['Ambiguous behavior for ClassNameGenerator::generateClassName'],['`ClassNameGenerator` has two variants for the `generateClassName` feature. One that takes a target `Class<?>` and another that takes a target `String`. I'm a bit confused by the concept of a target here and I think we should explain that a bit more in the javadocs.

