**Backported to:** [5.0.11](https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-framework/milestone/192?closed=1)
']",['closed'],[1],['**[Sam Brannen](https://jira.spring.io/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=sbrannen)** commented

