**Referenced from:** commits https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-framework/commit/df51ff03862c6a299f2ff243828ec23608899311, https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-framework/commit/1d8e5f4d853a51834710536efec72e6819ca9970
']",['closed'],[4],"[""**[Juergen Hoeller](https://jira.spring.io/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=juergen.hoeller)** commented

